content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4115.9 - Bad acting horse

State Regulations

The starter may excuse a bad acting horse prior to
passing the recall post. There will be no recall for a bad acting or off gait
horse after the recall post is passed. Notes
